data.description: NO HOA! Wow, you won't believe the space this property has to offer! On the first floor, you'll find a fantastic layout with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, along with a formal dining area. But wait, there's more! Head up to the second floor, and you'll be blown away by the sheer size of the bonus rooms. There's even an additional bathroom, an office space, and a room with a generously sized walk-in closet - it's like a hidden gem!And that's not all - this home sits on almost an acre of land, the back yard is surrounded by a sturdy chainlink fence for added privacy. The side entry garage makes parking a breeze, and there's even a large storage building on the property. Trust me, you have to see it in person to truly grasp the incredible space and features this home has to offer. It's a real gem that's waiting for the perfect owner!
